chanism comparing perpetual price to mark price. Long positions pay funding when rates are positive, receiving payment when negative. The Sui blockchain enables fast settlement with sub-second finality. Funding payments are automatically credited or debited from position margins without requiring manual intervention."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
